#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:114
msgid "Llama.cpp Backend"
msgstr "Llama.cpp engine"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:115
msgid ""
"Xinference supports models in ``gguf`` format via ``xllamacpp``. `xllamacpp "
"<https://github.com/xorbitsai/xllamacpp>`_ is developed by Xinference team, "
"and is the sole backend for llama.cpp since v1.6.0."
msgstr ""
"Xinference admite modelos en formato gguf a través de xllamacpp. `xllamacpp "
"<https://github.com/xorbitsai/xllamacpp>`_ es desarrollado por el equipo de "
"Xinference y se convierte en el único backend de llama.cpp a partir de "
"v1.6.0."

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:121
msgid ""
"Since Xinference v1.5.0, ``llama-cpp-python`` is deprecated. Since "
"Xinference v1.6.0, ``llama-cpp-python`` has been removed."
msgstr ""
"Desde Xinference v1.5.0, ``llama-cpp-python`` quedó obsoleto; a partir de "
"Xinference v1.6.0, este backend ha sido eliminado."

